div.h1: Why does user-agent.rawrify.com traffic bypass CloudFront?
div.div: CloudFront strips the user agent header from the client request before passing it on to Lambda, adding in its own "CloudFront" agent instead. This is useless to the end user, since it is not their actual user agent.
